respects:
Soft skills enhancement
Presentation skills,
Solution-oriented mindset
International Perspective
Public-speaking skills
Financial Management
Leadership Skills
International Team experience
SeIf-Awareness etc. An individual goes through an intense experience in those six weeks. They shape their journey themself, and the learning differs from person to person. In the end, the person becomes an all-rounder.
